<div id="page-landing" class="page active">
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-left">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">Islamophobia Studies — China Report</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        Islamophobia Weaponized as <em>State Security:</em> The Oppression of Uyghur Muslims in China
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        An investigation into how the Chinese state transforms Uyghur Muslim identity into a security problem — enforced through counterterrorism law, mass surveillance, detention, forced labor, and state propaganda.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-team">
        <div class="team-label">Research Team</div>
        <div class="team-names">Jaden Liu &nbsp;·&nbsp; Alan Fang &nbsp;·&nbsp; Abhinav Bellapu</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-right">
      <div class="hero-right-inner">
        <div class="hero-quote">
          <p>Islamophobia is not only fear at the individual level, but a structural system supported by institutions, law, security policy, and state power.</p>
          <cite>Prof. Hatem Bazian — Clash of Civilizations Lecture</cite>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-grid">
          <div class="stat-item">
